<BaseLayout title="How to Choose a Crypto Wallet? Hot Wallets vs Cold Wallets - 1H Crypto" lang="en" description="A comprehensive guide to choosing crypto wallets. Understand the difference between hot wallets and cold wallets, and which one suits your needs." activeNav="learn">
